>\r\n<ul class=\"messages\">\r\n<li class=\"notice-msg\"> \r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Please enable cookies in your web browser to continue.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"page-title\">\r\n<h1><a name=\"top\"></a>What are Cookies?</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Cookies are short pieces of data that are sent to your computer when you visit a website. On later visits, this data is then returned to that website. Cookies allow us to recognize you automatically whenever you visit our site so that we can personalize your experience and provide you with better service. We also use cookies (and similar browser data, such as Flash cookies) for fraud prevention and other purposes. If your web browser is set to refuse cookies from our website, you will not be able to complete a purchase or take advantage of certain features of our website, such as storing items in your Shopping Cart or receiving personalized recommendations. As a result, we strongly encourage you to configure your web browser to accept cookies from our website.</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"subtitle\">Enabling Cookies</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"disc\">\r\n<li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"#ie7\">Internet Explorer 7.x</a></li>\r\n<li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"#ie6\">Internet Explorer 6.x</a></li>\r\n<li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"#firefox\">Mozilla/Firefox</a></li>\r\n<li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"#opera\">Opera 7.x</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><a name=\"ie7\"></a>Internet Explorer 7.x</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Start Internet Explorer</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Under the <strong>Tools</strong> menu, click <strong>Internet Options</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"{{skin url=\"images/cookies/ie7-1.gif\"}}\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Click the <strong>Privacy</strong> tab</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"{{skin url=\"images/cookies/ie7-2.gif\"}}\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Click the <strong>Advanced</strong> button</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"{{skin url=\"images/cookies/ie7-3.gif\"}}\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Put a check mark in the box for <strong>Override Automatic Cookie Handling</strong>, put another check mark in the <strong>Always accept session cookies </strong>box</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"{{skin url=\"images/cookies/ie7-4.gif\"}}\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Click <strong>OK</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"{{skin url=\"images/cookies/ie7-5.gif\"}}\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Click <strong>OK</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"{{skin url=\"images/cookies/ie7-6.gif\"}}\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Restart Internet Explore</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"a-top\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"#top\">Back to Top</a></p>\r\n<h3><a name=\"ie6\"></a>Internet Explorer 6.x</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Select <strong>Internet Options</strong> from the Tools menu</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"{{skin url=\"images/cookies/ie6-1.gif\"}}\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Click on the <strong>Privacy</strong> tab</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Click the <strong>Default</strong> button (or manually slide the bar down to <strong>Medium</strong>) under <strong>Settings</strong>. Click <strong>OK</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"{{skin url=\"images/cookies/ie6-2.gif\"}}\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"a-top\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"#top\">Back to Top</a></p>\r\n<h3><a name=\"firefox\"></a>Mozilla/Firefox</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Click on the <strong>Tools</strong>-menu in Mozilla</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Click on the <strong>Options...</strong> item in the menu - a new window open</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Click on the <strong>Privacy</strong> selection in the left part of the window. (See image below)</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"{{skin url=\"images/cookies/firefox.png\"}}\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Expand the <strong>Cookies</strong> section</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Check the <strong>Enable cookies</strong> and <strong>Accept cookies normally</strong> checkboxes</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Save changes by clicking <strong>Ok</strong>.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"a-top\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"#top\">Back to Top</a></p>\r\n<h3><a name=\"opera\"></a>Opera 7.x</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Click on the <strong>Tools</strong> menu in Opera</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Click on the <strong>Preferences...</strong> item in the menu - a new window open</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Click on the <strong>Privacy</strong> selection near the bottom left of the window. (See image below)</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"{{skin url=\"images/cookies/opera.png\"}}\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>The <strong>Enable cookies</strong> checkbox must be checked, and <strong>Accept all cookies</strong> should be selected in the \"<strong>Normal cookies</strong>\" drop-down</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Save changes by clicking <strong>Ok</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"a-top\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"#top\">Back to Top</a></p>\r\n</div>','2011-03-31 01:49:18','2011-11-29 07:27:45',0,0,'','','','',NULL,NULL),(6,'公司简介','two_columns_left','','','help_6.html','','<div class=\"help\">\r\n<div class=\"help_l\">\r\n<div class=\"title\"><img src=\"{{media url=\"/help_title.gif\"}}\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n{{widget type=\"cms/widget_block\" template=\"cms/widget/static_block/default.phtml\" block_id=\"7\"}}\r\n<div class=\"help_l_bottom\"><img src=\"{{media url=\"/bottom_bg.gif\"}}\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"help_r\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h2>公司简介</h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>商城简介</strong></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>美德因我（www.MadeInWorld.cn）成立于2011年11月11日，是著名的西班牙LOGGOSS乐歌集团（www.loggoss.cn）旗下网上商城。</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p><img src=\"{{media url=\"/80KB_1.jpg\"}}\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"249\" /></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>乐歌诞生于人类所一直坚持的信仰，要实现乐歌所代表的美好愿望任重而道远。为此，乐歌搭建一个无缝对接的LOGGOSS全球平台以实现各种资源的整合利用，贸易、科技、教育、文化、慈善等活动都可以在这个平台上得到最广泛、最便捷、最完善、最自由、最平等和最透明的交流以及优势互补。</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>LOGGOSS（乐歌）总部位于西班牙著名港口、世界足球中心城市巴塞罗那，目前在全球21个国家和地区设立办公地点，建立全世界、功能和技术最为强大的乐歌全球贸易电子平台。</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>商业、慈善、共生互存，透明兼容，先行时代而诠释和谐，就是乐歌传承百年宿愿之初忠。2007年，乐歌基金诞生于西班牙。2010年,全球十九个国家同步实现运行,包括西班牙 、中国、英国、法国、德国、荷兰、葡萄牙、意大利、希腊、俄罗斯、加拿大、美国、阿根廷、巴西、智利、印度、阿联酋、澳大利亚、中国香港，成功打造一个技术最为强大的LOGGOSS全球贸易渠道运营平台，计划于2015年实现全球覆盖。</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p><img src=\"{{media url=\"/about2.jpg\"}}\" alt=\"\" width=\"752\" height=\"248\" /></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p><img src=\"{{media url=\"/100KB_1.jpg\"}}\" alt=\"\" width=\"754\" height=\"377\" /></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>美德因我电子商务秉承乐歌的全球国际贸易核心理念---中央仓储全新概念，借乐歌全球无缝链接供应链渠道优势，建立起极致压缩中间渠道的直销模式，降低渠道成本，以电子商务平台为桥梁，加强&ldquo;乐歌&rdquo;与消费端的互动，获得即时市场信息，进而根据反馈对市场信息做出快速反应；打破国际地域观念运用互联网迅速推广覆盖，足不出户将国际商品在全国推广销售。</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>公司拥有LOGGOSS国际工厂一站式服务平台、宁波北仑保税区中央仓储优势、承载仓储，集散，监控，调配的商贸运营需求，用世界顶级的英国SAGE（赛捷）管理软件和德国SAP（萨普）、法国CEGID（施易德）管理系统直线连接厂家和消费者，系统结合仓储，海关，保险，运输，银行，最大化节省中间运营成本。</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p><img src=\"{{media url=\"/150KB1.-2jpg.jpg\"}}\" alt=\"\" width=\"803\" height=\"512\" /></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p><img src=\"{{media url=\"/about5.jpg-2_1.jpg\"}}\" alt=\"\" width=\"766\" height=\"525\" /></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p><img src=\"{{media url=\"/about6.-2jpg.jpg\"}}\" alt=\"\" width=\"842\" height=\"546\" /></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>公司拥有国际级专业化的B2C操作团队、超前理念和鲜明定位等核心优势，采用中西结合的王道管理模式，诚信、品质、和谐、成就、共赢之核心价值观，商慈共生、和谐天成之超前理念，致力打造中国最大的进口商品网上商城，缔造乐歌MSB2C创新模式，解决进口商品和奢侈品国内价格明显高于国外的问题，让中国人以世界公民身份平价享受国际名品。</p>\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>关于我们</strong></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>我们是一支拥有国际化视野的专业化B2C操作团队，包括外籍专家、欧洲归国留学生、国内零售专家及行业精英等，我们都有先进的电子商务、连锁零售和规划理念，具有国内电子商务超专业化的操作能力，并能带来国际化的先进理念和产品概念。整个团队志同道合、优势互补、专心、专业、专注！</p>\r\n<img src=\"{{media url=\"/80KB2_1.jpg\"}}\" alt=\"\" /><br /> <br />\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>乐歌中国团队</strong></span></p>\r\n<br /> <img src=\"{{media url=\"/about8.jpg\"}}\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /> <br /><br /> <img src=\"{{media url=\"/80KB3_1.jpg\"}}\" alt=\"\" width=\"601\" height=\"429\" /><br />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>美德因我B2C团队</strong></span></p>\r\n<br /> <img src=\"{{media url=\"/about10.png\"}}\" alt=\"\" /><br /> <br />&nbsp; <img src=\"{{media url=\"/50KB_1.jpg\"}}\" alt=\"\" /><br /><br />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>国际团队介绍</strong></span></p>\r\n<br /> <img src=\"{{media url=\"/about12.jpg\"}}\" alt=\"\" /><br /><br /> <img src=\"{{media url=\"/about13.jpg\"}}\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div>','2011-05-26 07:28:49','2011-12-21 01:46:10',1,0,'','','','',NULL,NULL),(7,'原装进口查询','two_columns_left','','','help_7.html','','<div class=\"help\">\r\n<div class=\"help_l\">\r\n<div class=\"title\"><img src=\"{{media url=\"/help_title.gif\"}}\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n{{widget type=\"cms/widget_block\" template=\"cms/widget/static_block/default.phtml\" block_id=\"7\"}}\r\n<div class=\"help_l_bottom\"><img src=\"{{media url=\"/bottom_bg.gif\"}}\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"help_r\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h2>原装进口查询</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"yzcx\">\r\n<p>美德因我承诺: 我们销售的红酒都是 <span style=\"color: #880b0b;\">100%原装</span> &bull;<span style=\"color: #880b0b;\"> 原瓶</span> &bull; <span style=\"color: #880b0b;\">原产地进口</span>，您可以在下列查询框中输入每瓶红酒的sku编码 查询到红酒的相关信息，也可以选择登录网站<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://gepir.gs1.org/v31/xx/gtin.aspx?Lang=en-US\">http://gepir.gs1.org/v31/xx/gtin.aspx?Lang=en-US</a> 进行查询。祝您购物愉快。</p>\r\n<form id=\"GtinClient\" action=\"http://gepir.gs1.org/v32/xx/gtin.aspx?Lang=en-US\" method=\"post\"> <input id=\"__EVENTTARGET\" name=\"__EVENTTARGET\" type=\"hidden\" />\r\n<div class=\"select_input\"><input id=\"TabContainerGTIN_TabPanelGTIN_txtRequestGTIN\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\" maxlength=\"14\" name=\"TabContainerGTIN:TabPanelGTIN:txtRequestGTIN\" type=\"text\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"select_radio1\"><input id=\"TabContainerGTIN_TabPanelGTIN_rblGTIN_0\" checked=\"checked\" name=\"TabContainerGTIN:TabPanelGTIN:rblGTIN\" type=\"radio\" value=\"party\" /><label for=\"TabContainerGTIN_TabPanelGTIN_rblGTIN_0\">Trade Item Ownership</label><span class=\"ts\" style=\"